extends layout.pug

block content
  p.content.block
    | Hi there #{user.displayName},

  p.content.block
    | You are receiving this email because you requested a link to reset your password to access
    | the #[a(href=baseUrl) Bottom Time] application! Click the link below to complete the request!

  div.block.box.has-text-centered
    a(href!=resetPasswordUrl) Reset Password

  p.content.block
    | And, as a reminder, here is the username and email we have on file for you:

  div.block
    div.field.is-horizontal
      div.field-label
        label.label Username:
      div.field-body
        div.field
          p.control.is-expanded
            span.icon-text
              span= user.username
    div.field.is-horizontal
      div.field-label
        label.label Email Address:
      div.field-body
        div.field
          p.control.is-expanded
            span.icon-text
              span= user.email ? user.email : '<none>'

  p.content.block
    | Cheers,
    br
    | The Bottom Time Team!

  p.content.block.help
    | If you did not request this email and suspect something fishy is up then you can report this email
    | to #[a(href=`mailto:${adminEmail}`)= adminEmail].
